aria-labelledby="_WvPaYsXaJJ3j5NoP1eaa6AM168" id="_WvPaYsXaJJ3j5NoP1eaa6AM167" jsslot="" jsaction="CQwlrf" data-ved="2ahUKEwjF76Telo35AhWdMVkFHVWzBj0QpPYEKAB6BQjiAhAG" style="max-height: 0px;"><div class="xRFGCb Wt5Tfe M8CEed"><div id="faq_11"><div class="Xims0d"><span>SEO is the process of optimizing your website content and pages to generate more traffic from search engines. SEM goes beyond this to incorporate paid search ads. Both SEO and SEM should be part of your digital marketing strategy, as they both have their merits. SEO helps establish your online reputation in the long-term, so you will attract traffic continuously with evergreen content that connects with people at the top-of-the-funnel. SEM enables you to get quick results cost-effectively by driving conversions at the bottom-of-the-funnel.</span></div></div></div></div></g-accordion-expander></div></g-accordion></div></g-expandable-container></div></div></div></div><div class="NJo7tc Z26q7c"></div></div></div><div class="g Ww4FFb tF2Cxc" lang="en" style="width:600px" data-hveid="CIMBEAA" data-ved="2ahUKEwjF76Telo35AhWdMVkFHVWzBj0QFSgAegUIgwEQAA"><div class="jtfYYd" data-sokoban-container="ih6Jnb_PAkGCb"><div class="NJo7tc Z26q7c uUuwM jGGQ5e" data-header-feature="0"><div class="yuRUbf"><a href="https://www.reliablesoft.net/search-engine-marketing/" data-jsarwt="1" data-usg="AOvVaw1TM84V1infmLxLR5BW4WFI" data-ved="2ahUKEwjF76Telo35AhWdMVkFHVWzBj0QFnoECH0QAQ"><br><h3 class="LC20lb MBeuO DKV0Md">What is Search Engine Marketing (SEM)?
